---
import AppLayout from "../layouts/AppLayout.astro";
---

<AppLayout
  title="Send | Bore v2"
  description="Phase 1 send flow shell for Bore v2."
>
  <section class="panel">
    <p class="eyebrow">Send route</p>
    <h2>Create a transfer session</h2>
    <p>
      Phase 1 only lands the route, shell, and stack wiring. Session creation,
      typed clients, and file transfer behavior remain Phase 2 and beyond.
    </p>
    <div class="callout">
      <strong>Next milestone:</strong>
      <span>
        create and persist transfer sessions from the Elysia API with shared Zod
        contracts.
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>
</AppLayout>
